cs.DC, cs.CR, cs.DB, cs.SE, cs.CY 

This paper discusses compliance with data handling requirements in cloud storage systems, which involves aspects of distributed computing (DC), security and privacy (CR), databases (DB), software engineering (SE), and cybernetics (CY). However, since the paper focuses on the technical implementation of a transparent data handling layer in a distributed database, cs.DC and cs.DB are the most likely sub-categories.
